trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for selecting bitmap files in a property browser.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder et brukergrensesnitt for å velge punktgrafikkfiler i en nettleser for egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The BitmapEditor class provides a simple way to select a bitmap image for a property.
trans-unit.target: Klassen BitmapEditor er en enkel måte å velge punktgrafikk for en egenskap.

trans-unit.source: Starting the editor displays an **Open File** dialog box that allows directory navigation and selecting a file.
trans-unit.target: Start redigeringsprogrammet viser en **åpne filen** dialogboks der directory navigasjon og velge en fil.

trans-unit.source: The file list is initially filtered for bitmap (.bmp) files.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.BitmapEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.BitmapEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the extensions for the file list filter that the bitmap editor will initially use to filter the file list.
trans-unit.target: Henter filtypene for listen filfilter redigeringsprogrammet punktgrafikk opprinnelig vil bruke til å filtrere listen over.

trans-unit.source: The default set of file extensions used to filter the file list.
trans-unit.target: Standardsettet med brukes til å filtrere listen over filtyper.

trans-unit.source: Gets the description for the default file list filter provided by this editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter beskrivelsen for filen listen filtret standard av dette redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The description for the default type of files to filter for appears in the file list filter drop-down box.
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelsen for standard filtypen å filtrere etter vises i listen filter rullegardinlisten filen.

trans-unit.source: The description for the default type of files to filter the file list for.
trans-unit.target: Standard filtypen til å filtrere listen over filer for beskrivelsen.

trans-unit.source: Loads an image from the specified stream.
trans-unit.target: Laster inn et bilde fra den angitte strømmen.

trans-unit.source: The stream from which to load the image.
trans-unit.target: Dataflyten fra å laste inn bildet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Drawing.Image"></xref> loaded from the stream.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Drawing.Image"> </xref> er lastet inn fra dataflyten.
